doc.title: Nkatsakanyo wa xiengetelo xa Link Open With
doc.description:
Xiengetelo lexi xi ku pfumelela ku lawula hi ku olova ndlela leyi swihlanganisi swa le henhla swi pfuriwaka ha yona.

Fasitere: swihlamusela-marito swinâ€™wana, mafasitere lama humelelaka, mafasitere lamantshwa, mafasitere lamantshwa lama nga tiviwiki, fasitere ra sweswi (hi ntolovelo)

Tithebhu: ximatsi xa thebhu ya sweswi, thebhu ya sweswi, exineneni xa thebhu ya sweswi (xihlawulekisi)

Xiyimo xa ku tirha: a xi tirhi, tirhisa hi ku hatlisa (xihlawulekisi)
